data.description: Indulge in a lavish lifestyle at the pinnacle of sophistication in this top-floor haven nestled w/in the prestigious enclave of THE POINTE RESORT CONDOMINIUMS AT TAPATIO CLIFF. This 2-bed, 2-bath residence epitomizes modern luxury w/ its contemporary design, featuring the coveted dual master, split floor plan, each adorned w/ full ensuite baths for opulent comfort. As you enter, be captivated by the sweeping views of the Green Belt, Phoenix Mountains Preserve & awe-inspiring sunrises from the living room & bedrooms. Unwind by the beehive fireplace in the living room, complemented by custom stone trim for an exquisite touch. The gourmet kitchen is a masterpiece of culinary artistry, boasting updated cabinets, lighting, & appliances, along w/ opulent granite counters & a chic breakfast bar. This residence is a testament to refined living, meticulously designed to offer both comfort & grandeur. Immerse yourself in the resort-like ambiance of THE POINTE RESORT, where three pools, tennis, & basketball courts await your leisure. Situated in Central Phoenix, this home is surrounded by top-rated golf courses & provides easy access to hiking at Lookout Mountain, North Mountain, Piestewa Peak, & Dreamy Draw Recreation Areas. Elevate your lifestyle in this luxurious retreat that seamlessly combines comfort, style, & recreational opulence in the heart of Phoenix.
